                     <interp inst="t17870912-50-verdict238" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY Of stealing, but not in the dwelling house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17870912-50-punish239" type="punishmentDescription">
